        <Parent_String>people in history-related occupations [300168378], people in history and related occupations [300171567], social scientists [300171580], people in the social sciences and related occupations [300168333], people by occupation [300024980], people (agents) [300024979], People (hierarchy name) [300024978], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
